<div>
  <div class="bg-white">
    <h1 class="font-bold text-4xl mb-4 bg-green text-white px-6 py-8 text-center header-radius">Adoption Application</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="flex bg-slate-100 w-full p-6 rounded-xl">

    <div class="w-1/3 bg-white p-12 rounded-xl shadow-lg mr-5 ">
      <h2 class="font-semibold text-2xl mb-2">Select a Pet to Adopt:</h2>
      <%= render 'form', adoption_application: @adoption_application %>
    </div>

    <div class="relative w-2/3">
      <%= image_tag('dog.png', class: 'absolute top right-2 w-16 md:w-36 z-10' )%>
      <div class="w-full p-12 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg relative z-0">
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-2xl mb-2">Application Reminders:</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">Thank you for expressing interest in adopting a pet! To proceed with the adoption, please ensure your application is fully completed. Here’s how you can do it:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-5 ml-4">
          <li><strong>Select a Pet:</strong> Browse our listings and choose a pet you wish to adopt.</li>
          <li><strong>Review and Submit:</strong> Verify and submit your application.</li>
          <li><strong>Application Review:</strong> Your personal details will be shared to the concerned shelter to validate your application.</li>
          <li><strong>Requirements:</strong> The shelter will contact you through the chat for further verification and compliance. They might ask for personal details, living situation, and pet care experience. </li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-3">Once Approved:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-5 ml-4">
          <li><strong>Shelter Visit:</strong> Once your application is approved, visit the shelter to fetch your new friend.</li>
          <li><strong>Bring Identification:</strong> Ensure you bring a valid ID for identification purposes.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-3">Why Complete Your Application?</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-5 ml-4">
          <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> Follow the Animal Welfare Act of the Philippines (Republic Act No. 8485) to ensure pet safety and welfare.</li>
          <li><strong>Ensure Pet’s Welfare:</strong> Help us understand your home environment to place the pet in the best possible setting.</li>
          <li><strong>Efficiency:</strong> Comply with our review process to bring your pet home sooner.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl mb-3">Philippine Adoption Regulations</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-5 ml-4">
          <li><strong>Compliance with Animal Welfare Act:</strong> Provide proper shelter, food, and medical care for your adopted pet.</li>
          <li><strong>Home Visit:</strong> A visit may be scheduled to ensure your environment is suitable.</li>
          <li><strong>Adoption Fee:</strong> Fees may apply to support the care of other pets in need in the shelter.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>If you need assistance, you may contact the concerned shelter through our chat service. Thank you for being a part of our pet-loving community!</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
